Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:50.23,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.94,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we met in the hallway,
