Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mix them in right order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember you promised you wouldn't do any experiments home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have any choice? I can't mess up in the membership drive tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm black all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait till you lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't stacked any blocks for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Tomomi, couldn't she at least wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you locking me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry, Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you doing experiments  , we could lose all our potential new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let you out once the membership drive is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those four will lose out on other clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, they sure are dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wish we knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-kun! Mikage-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-wait! We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to... I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares. Let's get the new members in before she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on and have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sign up now, you'll get to go to a movie with the hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the track and field, Yamagishi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks you. Did we get any new members?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl members will double.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you throw in chocolate chip and mint ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can increase the member by five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Mikage-chan? You really want to sign up for track and field?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waitsec, Mikage. What about the chem club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chem club? But I have to join the track and field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me joining the track and field?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least if you can fill out the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When an object that weigh 40 kilo fall for 3 meters, the shock of landing will be 2.3G.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human bones should be able to withstand up to 4G in vertical shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Gotta hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you decide on the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm still trying to decide if I want to join...
Comment: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the tea ceremony club or the handicraft club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not another failure. It's theoretically perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Younger Matsunaga, did you get any new members?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the club is shut down, we wouldn't be able to do experiments as we like!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you circle around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've made flashy experiments like Matsunaga's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to expose our shame to the new recruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this keeps up, she'll get steamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Nobody's around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone atop the hill decorated by lilac, I wait for the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All by myself, all by myself... by Rumiko Daijoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like, Matsunaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you want to sign up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good collection of British literature, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But I haven't seen many people interested in British literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just literature, but everything about England. Then see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you remember to lock the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Matsunaga-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try lock me up again, I'll sue you guys for illegal confinement!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go see how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's almost time for the second run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and fetch me when it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the club is history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that sure looked like Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the clothes were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're doing the club work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you sign up for the track and field?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I join up to a club with stupid Noda as president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the travel club. I'm collecting for the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel? Me? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,England, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,England?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't what you are up to, but I, the club president, won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You signed up for the literature club too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play ignorant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only one who'd wear such shameful lacy clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's gotta be disguised as me and is signing up to all these clubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was you who signed up for the track and field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch this joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I find her, she'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi! Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's two Mikages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi! Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Why are there two of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mikage! She's fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I'm Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! What are you screaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matsunaga! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you run when I said stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Younger Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matsunaga sisters, why do you run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear both of them were Younger Matsunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage Matsunaga-kun, where are you? Come out. It's no use hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Younger Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, hold me tight. Hold my heart trembling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me hide out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Younger Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Younger Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Club president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Matsunaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Daijoji after me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun, did you see Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find her, tell me. She's in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God.. Gotta find her quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the track and field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now where's stupid Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-chan, did you see Tomomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Younger Matsunaga, why did you run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Matsunaga-san, why do you have to interfere with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-chan, did you see Tomomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Tomomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, Tomomi was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Younger Matsunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you knock it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And will you give up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you lie? Just you wait till the next exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, Younger Matsunaga!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Younger Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined the literature club!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, lost her again. Younger Matsunaga, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the membership drive is all screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, you're late because you were watching the flower, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ran, we could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the flower last year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the flower last year, with Kurashige-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, where are you going? Why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The red shoes I've got on are making me run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls,\N"Spring Wind Express."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far do I have to run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:11.56,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do, there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.89,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:18.10,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:34.75,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.04,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:51.55,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:57.98,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:05.03,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.78,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:14.70,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:20.12,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:26.63,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do, there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:33.10,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us are better then one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:24.61,credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ending Song\N"There has to be Both of Us"\N("Futarijanakya Dame Nano")\NBy Dio
